---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Crystal Group"
  description="Terms and conditions governing the use of crystalgroup.in and Crystal Logistic Cool Chain Ltd's cold chain services across India."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-secondary pt-32 pb-16 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-[860px]">
      <span class="font-body font-bold text-eyebrow uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent mb-4 block">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h1 text-primary leading-tight tracking-tighter">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-primary/40 mt-3">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="bg-primary py-16 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-[860px] font-body">

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 first:border-0 first:pt-0 first:mt-0">Introduction</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        These terms and conditions govern your use of crystalgroup.in and the services provided by Crystal Logistic Cool Chain Ltd ("Crystal Group", "we", "us"). By accessing our website or engaging our services, you agree to be bound by these terms in full.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website or services. We reserve the right to update these terms at any time, and continued use of our site constitutes acceptance of any changes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Services</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Crystal Logistic Cool Chain Ltd provides the following services across India:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Cold storage and temperature-controlled warehousing</li>
        <li>Portable cold storage containers — available for rental and purchase</li>
        <li>Refrigerated transportation and last-mile cold chain logistics</li>
        <li>Food processing and blast freezing facilities</li>
        <li>Related cold chain infrastructure and logistics services</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The availability and scope of services may vary by location. Please contact us for specifics applicable to your requirements.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Quotations &amp; Orders</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>All quotations are valid for 30 days from the date of issue unless otherwise stated</li>
        <li>Orders are confirmed only upon written acceptance by Crystal Group and, where applicable, receipt of the agreed advance payment</li>
        <li>All prices are subject to Goods and Services Tax (GST) at the rate applicable at the time of invoicing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Container Rental Terms</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>The minimum rental period for portable cold storage containers is 7 days</li>
        <li>Rental charges are computed from the date and time of container delivery to the customer's site</li>
        <li>The customer is fully responsible for the safety, security, and proper use of the container throughout the rental period</li>
        <li>Any damage to the container beyond normal wear and tear will be assessed and charged to the customer at cost of repair or replacement</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Liability</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Crystal Group is not liable for any indirect, consequential, incidental, or special losses arising from the use of our services or website</li>
        <li>Our maximum aggregate liability in connection with any service is limited to the total value of that specific service contract</li>
        <li>Events beyond our reasonable control — including natural disasters, floods, government restrictions, strikes, or other force majeure events — are excluded from our liability</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        All content on crystalgroup.in — including text, images, graphics, branding, logos, and design — is the intellectual property of Crystal Logistic Cool Chain Ltd and is protected under applicable Indian intellectual property laws.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Reproduction, distribution, or use of any content from this website without prior written permission from Crystal Group is strictly prohibited.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        These terms and conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India. Any disputes arising out of or in connection with these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Mumbai, Maharashtra.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        For any questions regarding these terms or our services, please contact us:
      </p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-1">Crystal Logistic Cool Chain Ltd</p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-1">601 Synergy Business Park, Sahakar Road</p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-1">Off Aarey Road, Goregaon East</p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">Mumbai, Maharashtra 400063</p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Email: <a href="mailto:marketing@crystalgroup.in" class="text-accent hover:underline">marketing@crystalgroup.in</a>
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
